[Dr Chotani raises some interesting possibilities. As mentioned, ergot has
been found worldwide (a sampling of recent identifications can be found in
the ProMED-mail archives mentioned in the "see also" section below). Given
the scant details we have available on this outbreak, this merits
consideration as part of the differential diagnosis. We await further
information on this outbreak from official sources. - Mod.MPP]
